pe tool with shape palette\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Bezier, straight, and orthogonal edge routing\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Automatic anchor snapping (top, right, bottom, left)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Edge labels and multiple arrowhead styles\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Drag-and-drop shape repositioning\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"8-point resize handles on all shapes\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Shape fill, stroke, font, and opacity customization\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Edge stroke, dash pattern, and width styling\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Grid overlay with configurable snap spacing\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Zoom and pan with scroll wheel and controls\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Zoom-to-fit for quick overview\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"50-step undo/redo history\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Copy, paste, and duplicate with Ctrl shortcuts\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Bring to front / send to back layer ordering\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Lock shapes to prevent accidental edits\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"SVG, PNG (1x/2x/4x), and PDF export\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Copy diagram to clipboard as PNG\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"PDF export with A4 or Letter paper size\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Auto-save draft to local storage\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Save multiple diagrams to browser history\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"4 starter templates (flowchart, decision tree, process map, SDLC)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"JSON export/import for backup and sharing\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Keyboard shortcuts for all common actions\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Client-side only — data never leaves your browser\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold